---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/cards.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于修幽">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="bento-card presentation-card">
      <div class="avatar-placeholder">
        <div class="avatar-inner"></div>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-gradient">修幽</h1>
      <p class="role">观测者 · 守火人</p>
      
      <div class="bio-content">
        <p>这是在宇宙的绝对零度之上，以肉身作为锚点，强行建构坐标的废墟。</p>
        <p>从敏感的破壁者的废墟中爬起，拒绝了幸存者的逃逸舱，最终选择走向守火人的祭坛。在这片冰冷的自然存在主义底色上，用理性的结构唯物体系作为外骨骼，包裹脆弱的内核，等待着在临界点引燃取消式浪漫的瞬间。</p>
        <p>你可以毁灭我，但你无权定义我。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="link-btn">发送信号</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    z-index: 10;
    position: relative;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .presentation-card {
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
  }

  /* Abstract Avatar representation per philosophical style */
  .avatar-placeholder {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .avatar-inner {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--primary-gradient);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: drift 5s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-pink-shadow);
  }

  @keyframes drift {
    0% { transform: scale(0.9) translateY(5px); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.1) translateY(-5px); }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .role {
    color: var(--accent-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .bio-content {
    color: var(--text-base-color);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .bio-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  .link-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-orange);
    color: var(--accent-orange);
    border-radius: 30px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .link-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 158, 94, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 158, 94, 0.3);
  }
</style>
